  <brief_title>Heart Rate Variability (HRV) Among Children With Brain Damage</brief_title>
  <official_title>Assessment of Autonomic Nervous System With Analysis of Heart Rate Variability in Children With Brain Damage.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
